{"tid":629403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞透視 國民待遇","createTime":"2018-04-14T16:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T09:05:48.000Z","uid":6582,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc02dc5c9f44d06b2e7326c49facd94b1401591","tid":629403,"uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IiGYxXcZjxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIiGYxXcZjxA&d=uFXFC5gL93sjN42CAb%2F3tzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5545cf7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IiGYxXcZjxA</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n幾好睇, 講到尾都係選擇, 取捨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n點揀都有好有唔好<br />\r\n<br />\r\n生活基本始終都關錢事, 個生意佬又好, 社工又好都算理性<br />\r\n唔會一面倒唱好大陸, 都講左有D 文化, 習慣要受<br />\r\n<br />\r\n不過講真同移民一樣, 其實你選擇左既都要去面對, 適應<br />\r\n<br />\r\n第1個社會講左重點, 搵既人工, 租金佔佢極少部分, 返香港租金要佔一半<br />\r\n第2個社工講得幾好, 如果本身無機會去接觸, 就會以返本身香港人自己眼光去睇野, 好似佢太太咁<br />\r\n<br />\r\n唔面對生活, 如果一味只係上網指樣樣都衰, 哂氣啦點點點<br />\r\n返到現實, 用呢種態度生活, 5年後既你, 係咪真係會有改善呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cafae29431461ed7eb4901661c6a549d85f2eef","tid":629403,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"會幾多「精英」返上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28bacc84f59dc1fbd131eaa1e5b0d43fb2fed32","tid":629403,"uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe495be01672fe6740d5032b3f9f40589e6ca0b","tid":629403,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f087e00b4a9de6dbf1646e681963a645c6e0b3c","tid":629403,"uid":119895,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"5毛開工了"},{"pid":"a5f28a635df